Abuja (Sundiata Post) – The newly sworn-in Governor of Yobe State Alh. Mai Mala Buni has appointed Alh. Baba Malam Wali mni as the Acting Secretary to the State Government. According to Abullahi Bego who signed as Director General Press Affairs to Gov. Mai Mala Buni said the appointment takes immediate effect. The acting SSG was until his new appointment the substantive Secretary to State Government under the immediate past Governor Ibrahim Gaidam’s administration. Details Later… Culled from The Nation